{"analytics_identifier":"OT1323","base_path":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles","content_id":"57f7737a-90e3-4e24-9de1-b4312830b4e7","description":"The Office for Zero Emission Vehicles (OZEV) is a team working across government to support the transition to zero emission vehicles (ZEVs). We are providing support for the take-up of plug in vehicles, as well as funding to support chargepoint infrastructure across the UK. This will contribute to economic growth and will help reduce greenhouse gas emissions and air pollution on our roads. OZEV is part of the Department for Transport and the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero .","details":{"acronym":"OZEV","alternative_format_contact_email":"ozev.enquiries@dft.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Office for Zero Emission Vehicles (OZEV) is a team working across government to support the transition to zero emission vehicles (ZEVs). We are providing support for the take-up of plug in vehicles, as well as funding to support chargepoint infrastructure across the UK. This will contribute to economic growth and will help reduce greenhouse gas emissions and air pollution on our roads.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Office for Zero Emission Vehicles\">OZEV</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-transport\">Department for Transport</a> and the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-energy-security-and-net-zero\">Department for Energy Security and Net Zero</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-transport","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Office for Zero Emission Vehicles"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/research","title":"Research at OZEV"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/1-billion-to-cut-costs-for-businesses-drive-growth-and-clean-up-uk-roads","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c418104a06660f0854420d/s712_commercial-ev-960.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c418104a06660f0854420c/s465_commercial-ev-960.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c41810b66ff902f45441f8/commercial-ev-960.png"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-25T00:01:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Zero Emissions Truck and Van grants and the Depot Charging Scheme aim to help businesses make the switch to electric vans and trucks.</p>\n</div>","title":"£1 billion to cut costs for businesses, drive growth and clean up UK roads"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/grant-boost-to-cover-almost-half-the-cost-of-installing-ev-chargers-for-households-and-businesses","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/699eb0aadb2401de164d6c9b/s712_electric-vehicle.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/699eb0aa6457311dafbbcc42/s465_electric-vehicle.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/699eb0aa6457311dafbbcc43/electric-vehicle.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-02-25T00:02:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Flat owners, landlords, renters and businesses will be able to get grants of up to £500 per charge point.</p>\n</div>","title":"Grant boost to cover almost half the cost of installing EV chargers for households and businesses"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/four-more-ev-models-qualify-for-3750-discount-under-electric-car-grant-as-government-pumps-an-extra-15-billion-into-the-switch-to-electric","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/692fe23f345e31ab14ecf904/s712_mini.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/692fe23fa245b0985f034442/s465_mini.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/692fe23f2a37784b16ecf8cb/mini.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-12-03T00:01:06.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Government doubles the number of models available for the top ECG discount.</p>\n</div>","title":"Four more EV models qualify for £3,750 discount under Electric Car Grant as government pumps an extra £1.5 billion into the switch to electric"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/new-sunderland-made-nissan-leaf-qualifies-for-3750-discount-under-governments-ev-grant-in-a-boost-for-north-east-manufacturing","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6920236cf8eba3d0e866f140/s712_leaf.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6920236c3735e57039f985fb/s465_leaf.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6920236c9c8e8f345bf985f6/leaf.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-21T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>There are now 39 models of electric vehicles eligible for the Electric Car Grant.</p>\n</div>","title":"New Sunderland-made Nissan LEAF qualifies for £3,750 discount under government’s EV grant in a boost for North East manufacturing"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/10-million-for-cutting-edge-tech-to-help-futureproof-englands-electric-vehicle-chargepoint-supply-and-keep-drivers-moving","image":{"alt_text":"Electric vehicle chargepoint.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690856e65e080b1224898116/s712_ev-charging-960.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690856e6ef26c341988b254c/s465_ev-charging-960.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690856e614e0c1d978417502/ev-charging-960.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-11-03T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Companies have until 25 March 2026 to apply for the funding.</p>\n</div>","title":"£10 million for cutting edge tech to help futureproof England’s electric vehicle chargepoint supply and keep drivers moving"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/public-electric-vehicle-chargepoints-surge-23-in-just-one-year","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690385c192779f89baa52030/s712_car_1.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690385c1e2ebc0fb39a5202f/s465_car_1.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/690385c1fabc9f10a832a895/car_1.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2025-10-30T15:31:48.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>There are now over 86,000 chargers on Britain’s roads, making it easier than ever for drivers to charge up and go. </p>\n</div>","title":"Public electric vehicle chargepoints surge 23% in just one year"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/plug-in-vehicle-grants/cars","title":"Electric Car Grant"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/electric-vehicle-chargepoint-grants","title":"Electric vehicle chargepoint grants"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/residential-chargepoints-eligible-vehicles","title":"Residential chargepoints: eligible vehicles"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/authorised-chargepoint-model-list","title":"Eligible EV chargepoint model list"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/electric-vehicle-chargepoint-installers","title":"Find an electric vehicle (EV) chargepoint installer"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"service","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":true,"organisation_type":"sub_organisation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"Our <a class=\"govuk-link brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/office-for-zero-emission-vehicles/about/personal-information-charter\">Personal information charter